        <section id="why-choose-us" class="card">
            <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Expertise and Experience:</strong> Seasoned professionals with a wealth of experience in finance and insurance.</li>
                <li><strong>Comprehensive Services:</strong> A wide range of services designed to address every aspect of your financial life.</li>
                <li><strong>Quality Assurance:</strong> Rigorous quality assurance processes to ensure the best advice and solutions.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="personal-note" class="card">
            <h2>A Personal Note</h2>
            <p>Having faced challenges in the past due to misleading information, I created LAYLOAN to ensure that no one else has to go through what I did. I want to help you on your journey to financial success.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing LAYLOAN. Together, we can build a brighter financial future for our community and country.</p>
